82.873, 182.6169, 183.9349, 184.7442, 185.4134, 184.817, 184.8813, 184.7509, 183.8254, 181.546, 180.1417, 179.0906, 182.6523, 181.8854, 181.2261, 181.9439, 182.3883, 182.8856, 182.3701, 181.8456, 182.3362, 181.955, 181.1988, 181.471, 182.8714, 183.0385, 183.1846, 183.1039, 182.7415, 182.3902, 182.8024, 183.6393, 182.4645, 181.7148, 181.2729, 179.7977, 179.5442, 179.6208, 179.1626, 178.3996, 176.6771, 176.3029, 177.9114, 176.9908, 177.3715, 176.4272, 172.7706, 172.8178, 171.0309, 169.3286, 167.6258, 167.87, 167.7721, 166.2651, 166.0256, 168.7668, 170.2714, 170.9277, 172.1906, 172.5105, 171.9848, 170.3974, 171.5986, 169.8694, 169.5759, 170.2355, 170.9556, 170.7367, 169.7602, 168.5574, 168.1513, 168.2816, 167.321, 168.5365, 167.6096, 167.2982, 165.573, 166.1466, 166.295, 166.0648, 163.8159, 162.9034, 164.8581, 164.377, 162.5101, 163.2097, 163.2361, 162.756, 163.6638, 163.0865, 162.1232, 163.4263, 163.0934, 160.7881, 162.1603, 162.0783, 160.9211, 160.1362, 156.7854, 155.982, 156.5154, 156.2061, 155.6554, 155.7865, 158.281, 159.6914, 160.3528, 160.2308, 159.7415, 164.1102, 164.7146, 161.9721, 161.1008, 160.7299, 159.3258, 158.9805, 159.9427, 158.8614, 157.8576, 157.7883, 158.7678, 158.6919, 160.5995, 158.6031, 160.954, 164.3691, 165.575, 162.8488, 161.3755, 161.2602, 164.155, 163.0755, 162.7177, 162.9558, 163.6352, 162.934, 163.4257, 164.4355, 164.4945, 163.9447, 165.4572, 170.8954, 176.5052, 174.2148, 176.3113, 183.4976, 185.21, 182.2749, 186.5168, 187.1279, 186.8565, 185.519, 185.8485, 183.1173, 186.269, 186.3488, 186.9244, 186.5471, 187.3904, 186.7025, null, null, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>时序信息中的Alpha -- 日内自相关/方差比/趋势强度因子</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略从分钟级行情数据中提取日内收益率和成交量占比的时序特征，构建衡量个股/品种日内价格自相关性的因子。核心逻辑是：日内价格序列的自相关性越强（即价格趋势越明显），信号越强。在商品期货中，高自相关性品种往往具有更强的趋势惯性，截面排名靠前的品种做多、靠后的做空，可以获得正收益。</p>\n<p>最优因子是 AR(1) 残差自相关系数（rho_comb），它在一阶回归后的残差上计算自相关，捕捉了被线性趋势掩盖的高阶持续性信息。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.73</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>3.0%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.2%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-12.8%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3447</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.19</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>-0.75</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.78 / 1.54</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.98</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.84</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.49</span></td><td>0.36</td><td>1.93</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.21</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.03</span></td><td>1.43</td><td>1.16</td><td>1.11</td><td>0.41</td><td>1.75</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.34</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.14</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.0</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>volume</code></td><td>成交量</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 分钟级（聚合到日频输出）</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 20 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 20 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3936</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.0%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>35.2</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>一阶自相关系数 (foc)</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\rho_1 = \\text{Corr}(r_t, r_{t-1}) = \\frac{\\sum_{t=2}^{n}(r_t - \\bar{r})(r_{t-1} - \\bar{r})}{\\sum_{t=1}^{n}(r_t - \\bar{r})^2}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">r_t</span> 为分钟级收益率。</p>\n<p><strong>Durbin-Watson 统计量 (DW)</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">DW = \\frac{\\sum_{t=2}^{n}(e_t - e_{t-1})^2}{\\sum_{t=1}^{n}e_t^2}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">e_t = r_t - \\bar{r}</span>。DW 越小，自相关越强。</p>\n<p><strong>AR(1) 残差自相关 (rho)</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">r_t = \\beta r_{t-1} + \\varepsilon_t, \\quad \\rho_{resid} = \\text{Corr}(\\varepsilon_t, \\varepsilon_{t-1})</div>\n<p>对回归残差 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\varepsilon_t</span> 计算自相关，捕捉被一阶回归忽略的高阶持续性。</p>\n<p><strong>因子日频聚合</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">F\\_Mean_{D_i} = \\frac{1}{n_s}\\sum_{j=1}^{n_s}F_j</div>\n<p>分别对收益率和成交量占比计算上述指标，等权合成为 comb 因子，再取过去 15 日滚动均值/标准差。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.12, 截面IC/时序IC均~0, 换手率1.32</td><td>原始报告逻辑直接移植，7因子+CS排名</td><td>信号在商品期货上几乎无效</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>发现因子方向需翻转（商品趋势逻辑与股票反转逻辑相反）</td><td>翻转foc方向(高自相关=趋势=做多)，降杠杆1.0，加TS z-score变体</td><td>Sharpe提升至0.35，时序IC出现(0.011)</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>最优变体foc_cs_flip=0.35，rho因子未充分利用</td><td><strong>关键转折</strong>: 对rho_comb(残差自相关)翻转方向+网格搜索hold/vol_target，加sym_rolling_ic_gate</td><td><strong>Sharpe跳至1.23</strong>，rho因子捕捉了被一阶回归掩盖的高阶趋势信号</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键发现</strong>: 原始研报针对A股，因子排序方向是\"高自相关→反转→低未来收益\"。但在商品期货中，高日内自相关意味着更强的趋势惯性，方向需要翻转。AR(1)残差自相关(rho)比原始一阶相关(foc)效果更好，因为它过滤了线性趋势，只保留高阶持续性信息。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 1分钟 K 线 → 日频因子 → 日频调仓</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货（58个品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 20 日换仓</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: </li>\n</ul>  - 分钟数据处理耗时较长（单轮~140-700秒）\n<p>- 2017年Sharpe为负（-0.25），该年商品市场波动较小 - 与因子库中 fangzheng_cora 因子相关性 0.41（临界值，非冗余） - 原始研报为A股因子，移植到商品需要翻转信号方向</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>ROLLING_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>15</code></td><td>daily factor smoothing window</td></tr><tr><td><code>ROLLING_MIN_P</code></td><td><code>5</code></td><td>min_periods for rolling mean</td></tr><tr><td><code>MIN_BARS</code></td><td><code>10</code></td><td>minimum minute bars per sym-day</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9993</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 28.61s</li>\n</ul>"}